<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF5D6AE2F7E19DCA1626B7DF" pageId="166" pageNumber="928" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF5D6AE2F7E19DCA1626B7DF" blockId="166.[2075,2668,2802,3229]" lastBlockId="166.[1464,2668,3239,3466]" pageId="166" pageNumber="928">
Subgenus Pyzonix; 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5D6AE2F6D99DCA179AB082" baseAuthorityName="Le Conte" baseAuthorityYear="1831" box="[2341,2458,2963,2992]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="166" pageNumber="928" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="lucifugus">lucifugus</taxonomicName>
species group. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5D6AE2F7E19DEE16CBB0EA" baseAuthorityName="H. Allen" baseAuthorityYear="1864" box="[2077,2251,2999,3032]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="166" pageNumber="928" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="evotis">Myotis evotis</taxonomicName>
is most closely related to M. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5D6AE2F7A89DBE16DAB732" authorityName="G. S. Miller" authorityYear="1897" box="[2132,2266,3047,3072]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="166" pageNumber="928" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="thysanodes">thysanodes</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5D6AE2F70D9DBE176EB732" baseAuthorityName="Merriam" baseAuthorityYear="1895" box="[2289,2414,3047,3072]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="166" pageNumber="925" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="keenii">M. keenii</taxonomicName>
, M. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5D6AE2F6409DBE1421B732" authorityName="Hollister" authorityYear="1909" box="[2492,2593,3047,3072]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="166" pageNumber="928" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="occultus">occultus</taxonomicName>
, and the paraphyletic 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5D6AE2F6EF9A5C17BAB714" baseAuthorityName="Le Conte" baseAuthorityYear="1831" box="[2323,2490,3077,3110]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="166" pageNumber="938" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="lucifugus">M. lucifugus</taxonomicName>
(specifically M. lL carissimus and M. l. pernox, which likely represent distinct species), although relationships among these species and the clade including 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5D6AE2F9629AFE1922B7F6" authorityName="G. S. Miller &amp; G. M. Allen" authorityYear="1928" box="[1694,1826,3239,3268]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="166" pageNumber="928" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="sodalis">M. sodalis</taxonomicName>
, M. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5D6AE2F8989AFE19B6B7F6" baseAuthorityName="H. Allen" baseAuthorityYear="1866" box="[1892,1974,3239,3268]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="166" pageNumber="928" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="volans">volans</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5D6AE2F8349AFE166EB7F6" baseAuthorityName="Le Conte" baseAuthorityYear="1831" box="[1992,2158,3239,3268]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="166" pageNumber="928" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="lucifugus">M. lucifugus</taxonomicName>
, M. L. relictus, and M. I. alascensis are not well resolved. Six subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
